data.description: Meticulous custom home on a corner lot! Newer roof, new water heater, main water line replaced! One of a kind lighting system, pre-wired for high-speed computer system, well maintained 3/4 inch Cherry washed birch flooring, vaulted ceilings, custom upper end appliances, Birch cabinets, deep kitchen sink, lots of countertop storage, and even a lit appliance garage! Outside features 6x34 covered Porch! Fenced backyard with garden area, full automatic sprinklers. Within minutes to Mtn Home & Mountain Home AFB. Make this custom home yours NOW before it's gone!!!!!
